<p>President Trump said he is immediately ending temporary deportation protections for Somali migrants in Minnesota, the U.S. state with the largest Somali community, in a Friday night announcement [theguardian.com#1][firstpost.com#1]. The protections are part of Temporary Protected Status (TPS), a program Congress created in 1990 to prevent deportations to countries facing disasters or conflict [thehindu.com#1]. While the policy targets Somali nationals, most Somalis in Minnesota are American citizens [straitstimes.com#1].</p><img src='https://kagiproxy.com/img/dfeLWAXkJsMxE7KdrgSKS-_zztwcqC8c2KHgfcu2Uc7PdYvIUVsYoHyyyZESRgHdN1CsxznWrjIDMxbagDh_LxmaT1RJ_ccrirmEJ0ieondbvXL0tU7wETUDTfB-gXMJtLJLmpop8g4GOngv9Zdb0NRri9DCLyy9qD66VTWaQK3YLX89alelxhmi7jMSQiJ4mLETvMz60gLn_T9vmVn9CpkWrqy1anG9EZUrwBIDYSlabp8-ab-5Y7jysPY7xO6S0g' alt='President Trump speaks at an event amid a policy announcement affecting Somali migrants in Minnesota' /><br /><h3>Highlights:</h3><ul><li>What changed: The President said he is immediately terminating temporary legal protections for Somali migrants in Minnesota [theguardian.com#1][firstpost.com#1]</li><li>Program purpose: TPS was created by Congress in 1990 to prevent deportations to countries suffering natural disasters, civil strife or other dangerous conditions [thehindu.com#1]</li><li>Minnesota context: Minnesota hosts the nation’s largest Somali community, many of whom fled Somalia’s long civil war [theguardian.com#1]</li><li>Citizenship reality: Most Somalis in Minnesota are American citizens and thus not subject to deportation under TPS changes [straitstimes.com#1]</li><li>Stated rationale: The President cited security concerns, alleging Somali gangs were harming the state and claiming large financial losses [firstpost.com#1]</li></ul><h3>Perspectives:</h3><ul><li>President Trump: He said he would immediately terminate temporary legal protections for Somali migrants in Minnesota, citing security concerns [theguardian.com#1][firstpost.com#1] (<a href='https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2025/nov/21/trump-protections-somalis-minnesota'>The Guardian; Firstpost</a>)</li><li>U.S. Congress (program intent): Congress created TPS in 1990 to prevent deportations to countries facing disasters, civil strife, or other dangerous conditions [thehindu.com#1] (<a href='https://www.thehindu.com/news/international/trump-says-hes-terminating-legal-protections-for-somali-migrants-in-minnesota/article70310253.ece'>The Hindu</a>)</li><li>Somali Americans in Minnesota: Most members of the community are U.S. citizens and therefore not directly affected by TPS changes [straitstimes.com#1] (<a href='https://www.straitstimes.com/world/united-states/trump-says-he-is-ending-temporary-deportation-protections-for-somalis-in-minnesota'>The Straits Times</a>)</li></ul><h3>Sources:</h3><ul><li><a href='https://www.straitstimes.com/world/united-states/trump-says-he-is-ending-temporary-deportation-protections-for-somalis-in-minnesota'>Trump says he is ending temporary deportation protections for Somalis in Minnesota</a> - straitstimes.com</li><li><a href='https://www.thehindu.com/news/international/trump-says-hes-terminating-legal-protections-for-somali-migrants-in-minnesota/article70310253.ece'>Trump says he’s terminating legal protections for Somali migrants in Minnesota</a> - thehindu.com</li><li><a href='https://www.firstpost.com/world/trump-terminates-temporary-deportation-protections-for-somalis-in-minnesota-citing-security-concerns-13952995.html'>Trump terminates temporary deportation protections for Somalis in Minnesota, citing security concerns</a> - firstpost.com</li><li><a href='https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2025/nov/21/trump-protections-somalis-minnesota'>Trump says he is ending immigration protections for Somalis in Minnesota</a> - theguardian.com</li></ul>